dfischer.utils

Interface WebSocketPluginInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericPluginInterface

    public interface WebSocketPluginInterface
extends GenericPluginInterface
    Allows to define fixed configuration settings for web socket plug-ins.
    See Also:
    GenericPluginInterface.TYPE_LOADTEST_EXEC, LoadtestPluginContext, LoadtestPluginFixedUserInputField
